{"tid":1655574,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"你地剩係支持黃店餐廳 咁其他舖頭點?","createTime":"2019-10-15T06:32:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-28T17:15:33.000Z","uid":61886,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"e242aba5a19205fb713f2d79c9661e056636a0f1","tid":1655574,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T06:32:29.000Z","msg":"除左餐廳之外<br />\n仲有好多唔同行業既黃店架<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢地都好需要大家支持<br />\n我地要建立黃店商業圈<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我自己簡單咁睇左幾區<br />\n列左幾區既黃店比大家參考下<br />\n以後大家想買野之前<br />\n睇下附近有無相關既黃店支持一下!<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nLink如下:<br />\n【終極整合】黃藍商戶地圖 (持續更新中)<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/maps/7q3dQpWAPW67BqcZ8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fmaps%2F7q3dQpWAPW67BqcZ8&d=P9V%2Fg5HR%2BYIczjwvlITT9JnDgp1V90hxAqV0yKYrtpw%3D&h=e8d8f1f7\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/maps/7q3dQpWAPW67BqcZ8</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>連鎖黃店:</ins></strong><br />\n阿布泰國 (百貨)<br />\n彌明生活百貨 (護膚美容)<br />\nA piece of Organic (護膚美容)<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>地區黃店<br />\n大埔: </ins></strong> <br />\n美蘭海味湯料Prettylandherbal (海味湯料)<br />\nH.Hairport Hair Salon (髮型屋)<br />\nHello Candy 美蘭茶 (花茶)<br />\nLuna韓國雜貨 (百貨)<br />\n18 Toyscorner (成人用品)<br />\nSo Lady Accessories <br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>屯門:</ins></strong><br />\n針魂入墨 (刺青)<br />\nLano Eyewear (眼鏡)<br />\nPhonebox手機維修 (手機維修)<br />\n超譯電話卡 (電話卡)<br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong>元朗天水圍:</strong></ins><br />\nThe Beast Fest (肉類及海鮮食材)<br />\nBring me Home (售賣機)<br />\n天姿作圍 (非牟利)<br />\n夾上癮 (售賣機)<br />\nDog Side Pet Shop (寵物用品)<br />\nGame Zone遊戲地帶<br />\n生活書社 (書局)<br />\nBook Castle (書局)<br />\nNaLotus (汽車保養)<br />\n天下貓貓一樣貓 (寵物用品)<br />\n<br />\n利申:<br />\n本人、本人親屬及朋友未有經營以上店舖<br />\n<br />\nPS. 幫襯前記得再FC"},{"pid":"14107e887e2e1079dbdee85325fbaa6db833fa48","tid":1655574,"uid":61886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"re